    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the philosophical arguments a bit more? Like, maybe touch on some specific ideas from thinkers like John Stuart Mill or even more modern libertarian perspectives on why state intervention is inherently harmful to the \"marketplace of ideas\"?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
